      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. Mechanically, it is sound, with a smooth-running engine and a responsive transmission that makes for a dependable daily driver. The exterior still looks great, though a close inspection will reveal some minor stone chips on the front bumper and a few light surface scratches consistent with careful use. Inside, the cabin is clean and all electronics are fully functional, offering a comfortable and honest representation of a quality used car.",
