    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are proud to present this impeccably preserved specimen, an automotive investment that transcends the standard pre-owned market. This vehicle exhibits a flawless aesthetic and mechanical profile, indicative of a history defined by meticulous stewardship and climate-controlled storage. From the depth of its original luster to the pristine condition of its interior appointments, every detail remains in showroom-state. This is a rare opportunity for the discerning collector to acquire a benchmark-level vehicle that represents the absolute pinnacle of its class.",
      "price": 46500.0,
